{"tid":2336951,"cid":38,"subCid":0,"title":"係外國比人問你係唔係Chinese你點答(2)","createTime":"2020-12-23T03:50:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-23T04:01:17.000Z","uid":36861,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"16fa74b8a8750b8100475864ae04cd494a0c2691","tid":2336951,"uid":36861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T03:50:21.000Z","msg":"係外國比人問你係唔係Chinese你點答(1)<br />\n傳餸門<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <a href=\"https://lih.kg/aGRhJaU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/aGRhJaU</a><br />\n<br />\n上集------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n緊係唔係啦, 今時今日仲當香港人係Chinese係咪要去check下個腦?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n文化唔同, 節日唔同, 收入唔同, 學識唔同, 觀念唔同, 食既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔同, 文字唔同, 語言<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dllm.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔同(唔係口音呀下), 連書面語都唔同, 道德倫理觀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔同, 教育唔同, 歷史背景香港又長過宜家所謂既支那幾倍...如果你咁都講得出話係, 又話者話咩中國一部份乜乜乜, 好心你地就唔好講啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />..<br />\n<br />\n打個比如, 英國人, 美國人, 澳洲人, 佢地食又差唔多, 語言一樣, 文化又share. 道德倫理觀又差唔多, 咁佢地係咪一樣既人?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你試下係New York地鐵站口指入個美國佬同佢講you are british you are british. are you british? you look so british to me...<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇下你有無本事企住行入地鐵站....<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/fan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以你地如果連自己係咩人都唔知, 自己身份都唔知, 唔好話傻仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 你地連狗都不如.<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n上集------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n估唔到1001左...真係痴線嫁你地班連登仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然唔知仲有無人想傾, 不過都係開個(2)先 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好似都係要開個正負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />I am Hongkonger (I use English because I do not want those cina dog see it..)<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我係支那人呀hi <br />\n<br />\nBTW, 雖然宜家係黑暗既日子, 但係都希望大家有個開心既聖誔, 係呢幾日咩都唔好諗, 同心愛既囡囡或仔仔出去開心下, 雖然唔可以返日本鄉下 (我好掛住我北海道個老婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />), 但大家頂住呀。<br />\n<br />\n幫香港祈個靚禱先, 我日日都會幫祈嫁, 你地如果係耶撚都日日祈下, 我會每日香港時間早上八點祈, 大家一齊! <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/as